channel.title: Scronix: Cammy PvP
channel.description:
Hey guys,
I'm here because I (obviously) need one or two people that are willing to help me develop a cammy pvp server. I looked back at some of the threads and there were several cammy pvp ones, which motivated me to start one (again) aswell. I still have my own server files which are from the same revision, but with a lot of upgrades, which we will be using. I will provide as much information about the current server files as you want on Skype.
Just leave a message here with your Skype (or via PM) and I'll contact you as soon as possible :)!
